snippet.title: Season 13 New Role 'Paparazzi' 📹
snippet.description:
"Too much curiosity makes money!"

Meet our new role, Paparazzi! ⭐

She seeks interesting news, information, gossips, and etc. to make money!
What will be the information she got?!

Play as Paparazzi to win the game! 🤩

#mafia42 #mafia #mobilegame
